title: Add the location 149,-60 to the Points of Interest
body:
> by 0x3cb9e515e2452937b501734aa2cc8ea673c28f27 (decentrafun)

## Decentrafun Complex

![Decentrafun Complex](https://api.decentraland.org/v1/parcels/149/-60/map.png)

Should the scene located at 149,-60 be added to the Point of Interest list?

## Description

We are developing many projects such as Wednesday talks about DCL and crypto art, sponsoring artists in the gallery, and developing a game to further bring attractions to DCL. We are also connecting with rarible and art professors to have curated art

**[Vote on this proposal on the Decentraland DAO](https://governance.decentraland.org/en/proposal/?id=7d227d80-c550-11eb-8d39-ebf2dfa350ad)**
